flowRoot.flowPara: Notes can be stored locally, on an email account, or through ownCloud. Additional storage locations can be added through the online accounts settings.
Please confirm the new location for your notes. Your existing notes will be moved to the new location.
Your notes have been successfully moved to the new location.
Select where you want to import notes from.
Tomboy and gnote notes are automatically detected and listed. If neither are found, only "Select Folder..." is shown as an option.
The import button becomes sensitive once an option is selected.
Next button becomes sensitive if the storage option is changed.
